Class GitBranchResponse.BranchRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.nyu.cs.javagit.api.commands.GitBranchResponse.BranchRecord

    GitBranchResponse

    public static class GitBranchResponse.BranchRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    A record containing branch, its head SHA1, and the comment of the commit on head. A list of this object is returned as a part of BranchResponse object when verbose option is set.
